text: Raghunathapuram is a village located in Nalgonda district, Telangana, India. This village is 12 km from the famous hill temple Yadagirigutta. This village has population of 6,000. This village is famous for manufacturing cloth material of variety designs and exports to other parts of the world. Category:Villages in Nalgonda district
title: Raghunathapuram, Nalgonda district
